{"tid":480392,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"熟勞工法，麻煩幫一幫手","createTime":"2017-11-26T06:23:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-26T08:59:58.000Z","uid":136832,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0c282c0a913ae3680e7a96121e44996c469632b7","tid":480392,"uid":136832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T06:23:03.000Z","msg":"我老豆係間公司做左7年裝修工人，<br />\n但無簽過合約，又無供強積金，其實雇主係未已經犯法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我老豆仲想拎埋長期服務金，但無簽合約，出糧仲要係出現金，無銀行紀錄，仲會唔會拎到？"},{"pid":"61030483b5008683a1afd58d7c14b6560295b962","tid":480392,"uid":80866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T06:37:07.000Z","msg":"唔會 rip"},{"pid":"ecedc905bba5420d8cab3c39a22935ec3fc06b8b","tid":480392,"uid":50801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T06:39:42.000Z","msg":"咩紀錄都冇，掉轉頭點證明你係員工？"},{"pid":"1ccd24f9860882fca266b2a34b407a5d6f58af2d","tid":480392,"uid":85819,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T06:49:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9030e69efad5094c9133b14983c59a72bd71cb8f","tid":480392,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T06:50:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53b00e5e4a0850ccce9ccdce463e48af5d433e1c","tid":480392,"uid":24443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T06:51:56.000Z","msg":"你老豆想笑撚死人咩"},{"pid":"e031833b5ea7bc4924c875ccb58a2fa7d2dd1e6b","tid":480392,"uid":13333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T06:52:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢無幫你供強積金 你老豆又無交稅<br />\n<br />\n打和啦<br />\n<br />\n搞大佢大家都無好處   唔通你想你老豆坐監咩</blockquote><br />\n好現實 但冇錯"},{"pid":"66bf96fa57cd54d885cbad751e3a0f59598331f4","tid":480392,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T06:56:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e96f8d6a4c653a36b0a37fedd575953e91c28734","tid":480392,"uid":136832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T07:26:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢無幫你供強積金 你老豆又無交稅<br />\n<br />\n打和啦<br />\n<br />\n搞大佢大家都無好處   唔通你想你老豆坐監咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢有報稅，無隱瞞到<br />\n個老細仲要5年無加過人工"},{"pid":"3a6b3237c53be3ba3c1f685f819bbc3659d9991b","tid":480392,"uid":121131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T07:31:53.000Z","msg":"日工定月薪工"},{"pid":"c4a09745146775743f7a89d186f3fee6aa939616","tid":480392,"uid":136832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T07:39:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日工定月薪工</blockquote><br />\n月薪工"},{"pid":"90acc22400581af21112108f48ab5b786fdef0be","tid":480392,"uid":121131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T07:47:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>日工定月薪工</blockquote><br />\n月薪工</blockquote><br />\n裝修出月薪咁有趣?<br />\n如果你阿爸唔怕同佢個老闆死過<br />\n你就印定哂佢番咁多年工嘅月曆出黎<br />\n叫佢記錄好邊日有番邊日無<br />\n記得計佢啲年假大假，有請無請<br />\n你阿爸要記熟佢<br />\n之後唔做之後帶齊資料上勞工處就可以了"},{"pid":"231a90c54962e261e6dd15d66dd65754a5dc4922","tid":480392,"uid":121131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T07:50:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>日工定月薪工</blockquote><br />\n月薪工</blockquote><br />\n裝修出月薪咁有趣?<br />\n如果你阿爸唔怕同佢個老闆死過<br />\n你就印定哂佢番咁多年工嘅月曆出黎<br />\n叫佢記錄好邊日有番邊日無<br />\n記得計佢啲年假大假，有請無請<br />\n你阿爸要記熟佢<br />\n之後唔做之後帶齊資料上勞工處就可以了</blockquote><br />\n不過前設係你阿爸間公司係正統有得賠先得<br />\n如果你阿爸個老闆根本無開公司 或者細公司唔怕你追數就會好難搞"},{"pid":"62212dbb09b03f6461f036851717db32228a0618","tid":480392,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T07:51:42.000Z","msg":"長期服觔金對沖完你老豆拎到幾多呀？收番埋啦"},{"pid":"e9c029d98b9b325d80a4bfd8e79da1e9b456ef5c","tid":480392,"uid":121131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T07:52:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>長期服觔金對沖完你老豆拎到幾多呀？收番埋啦</blockquote><br />\n佢老闆應該無供老強，唔洗對沖"},{"pid":"c537e28bbacba2b9297703d63ab795ef0283c6d3","tid":480392,"uid":13333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco